The '''Third Ring Apartment Towers''' was an apartment complex on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]], located twenty minutes by [[Air taxi/Legends|air taxi]] to the northeast of the [[Senate Building/Legends|Senate Building]]. It was at least 248 stories tall. [[Kinman Doriana/Legends|Kinman Doriana]] lived in an apartment on the 238th level.

